  Jane sparked a frenzy on her Instagram following her latest sizzling holiday snap. She told her 252,000 followers: “I hope you are all having a beautiful day! “The sun is out, the summer heat has arrived, and the pool is looking tempting! “Love the versatility of this beautiful scarf! It can be dressed up or down like this,” she added, referring to the all-blue ensemble. Jane wore the blue and turquoise patterned scarf as a flattering wrap around skirt. She paired it with a powder blue, strappy top and some barely-there, neutral toned heels.  